## Diagnostics

```{r pva, fig.height=7}
pva <- bind_rows(
  tibble(model = "Linear regression", actual = y_te, pred = pred_lm),
  tibble(model = "Elastic net",       actual = y_te, pred = pred_gn),
  tibble(model = "XGBoost",           actual = y_te, pred = pred_xgb),
